    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a small bowl<strong> </strong> – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
