    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze your pouch[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>of<strong> cooked white long grain rice </strong>to separate the grains</p><p>Tear the top corner of the pouch[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(just a little!) and <strong>microwave </strong>for 2 min or until piping hot</p><p>Tip: If you're cooking two or more pouches, pop them in together but increase the microwave cook time accordingly</p>",
